# option-class-ending patterns compete with name-ending ones by recency
frame .b1 Button
add *Foreground magenta widgetDefault
get .b1 foreground Foreground
optclear
add *foreground red widgetDefault
add *Foreground magenta widgetDefault
get .b1 foreground Foreground
optclear
add *Foreground magenta widgetDefault
add *foreground red widgetDefault
get .b1 foreground Foreground
